 character, including `__________` (ten spaces), `aaaaaaaaaa` (ten latin letter \"a\"s) or `üêà üêà üêà üêà üêà üêà üêà üêà üêà üêà` (ten cat emoji). These passwords are equivalent in their strength.\n\nWe can not prevent users from selecting weak passwords. We make reasonable efforts (including a minimum  password lengths and a blacklist of the most common user passwords) to encourage users to select better passwords, but it is ultimately their responsibility to select strong passwords.","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-07-23T17:44:16.177Z","updated_at":"2017-07-23T17:44:16.177Z","actor":{"username":"epriestley","cleared":false,"url":"/epriestley","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/000/043/3ebca5250ea5abd54b49ccc9d69c636af4585b2e_original.jpg/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"phabricator","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":1861153,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::AgreedOnGoingPublic","message":"","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-07-23T20:32:20.621Z","updated_at":"2017-07-23T20:32:20.621Z","first_to_agree":true,"actor":{"username":"iamnot1337","cleared":false,"url":"/iamnot1337","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/180/119/9cfd159ba45d57951ffc7ba7aaed2913f7108639_original.jpeg/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":null},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"phabricator","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":1861155,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"A limited Public Disclosure please.","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-07-23T20:34:58.711Z","updated_at":"2017-07-23T